Author: ratboi213
Text: Wow, thank you for responding to this old post! I’m still going through it so it means a lot to know that because I had no clue that upping the dose could help. I have an appointment with my dr next week so I’ll bring it up thank you :)

Author: PacoOnReddit
Text: Hi so just a random thought through my personal experience that was very similar, i didn’t see much help until my Zoloft dosage was upped to 100mg so I’d say not to be shut off to the idea of increasing dosage to get intended results
